string.name: NumberType_description
string.value: Calculate the sum of two given numbers: x+y.The maximum length of input data is 16.

string.name: StringBoolType_description
string.value: String character data str1 and str2 are concatenated, and the bool type controls the relative position.The maximum length of input data is 16.

string.name: ArrayType_description
string.value: Enter the array items one by one, confirm the key to add the data to the array, reset the key to clear the array data, and reverse the conversion key to reverse the order of the input array data.The maximum length of input data is 16.

string.name: ArrayType_input1
string.value: Enter a value for the array item

string.name: ArraybufferType_description
string.value: Assign the values of num1 and num2 to arraybuffer and square native, and then print arraybuffer on the arkts side.The maximum length of input data is 4.

string.name: ObjectType_description
string.value: Give basic personal information and construct a self-introduction statement.The maximum length of input data is 4.

string.name: date_type_description
string.value: Click the Get Time button to retrieve the current time of Date type from the native side. Click the conversion button to convert the obtained date into total milliseconds.
